metadata.description:
“Landscape” is a soundtrack to anyone getting their yard cleaned and landscaped. 

     Land, like water, is always in motion. Our daily interactions with different landscapes are vast. 

     This track is inspired by the movement of land and how a beautiful landscape can move you to be creative. The landscape of music and art is in a beautiful space right now. New ideas and brand-new landscapes to explore! 

Make sure you cut that grass though! 
Respectfully.

Artwork by MEGA

lyrics.text:
Envision where you want to be.

Think about the landscape.

All the specific things in your landscape.

Envision your self in that landscape.

Where you want to be.

See and feel your self there.

How will you feel once you are there.

Then start to dance to LANDSCAPE
